OL,3,CLab-grown coral could save the vibrant
OL,4,Cocean landscape
OL,6,FThe artificial technique involves
OL,7,Fmatching the conditions of the tank to
OL,8,Fthose where reefs are found in the
OL,9,Fwild and simulating the moon and sun
OL,10,Fcycles, ITV News Science Correspondent
OL,11,FMartin Stew reports
OL,13,FScientists are working to protect and
OL,14,Fsave ocean coral through a pioneering
OL,15,Fbreeding programme.
OL,17,FThe ocean animal which roots to the
OL,18,Fsea floor, is being bred in at a lab,
OL,19,Fmore than 70 miles from the nearest
OL,20,Fcoast, to reproduce on cue.
