OL,3,CLab-grown coral could save the vibrant
OL,4,Cocean landscape
OL,6,FReefs are ecologically extremely
OL,7,Fvaluable but have been deteriorating
OL,8,Fdue to mass bleaching events, climate
OL,9,Fchange and over fishing.
OL,11,FDr Michael Sweet from the University
OL,12,Fis a leading coral researcher who
OL,13,Fcreated the technique.
OL,15,FHe sees it as vital to understand the
OL,16,Freproduction process of coral
OL,17,Fecosystems to save those like the
OL,18,Fworld famous Great Barrier Reef in
OL,19,FAustralia.
