OL,3,CLab-grown coral could save the vibrant
OL,4,Cocean landscape
OL,6,FThe annual process is rarely seen by
OL,7,Fhumans, but the team at the University
OL,8,Fhave been able to create a technique
OL,9,Fwhich encourages coral to breed as
OL,10,Fprompted.
OL,12,FThe artificial technique involves
OL,13,Fmatching the conditions of the tank to
OL,14,Fthose where reefs are found in the
OL,15,Fwild and simulating the moon and sun
OL,16,Fcycles.
OL,18,FAfter spawning scientists will then
OL,19,Fmix the eggs to enable them to
OL,20,Ffertilise.
