OL,6,FThis could be a game changer in
OL,7,Fprotecting the reef animal as it could
OL,8,Fincrease the possibility of scientists
OL,9,Fcreating corals at aquariums to later
OL,10,Fbe released in the wild.
OL,12,FReefs are vital not only for the ocean
OL,13,Fecosystem and food chain but also
OL,14,Fenvironmentally too.
