OL,3,CLab-grown coral could save the vibrant
OL,4,Cocean landscape
OL,6,FLead principal investigator of the
OL,7,FAquatic Research Facility at Derby
OL,8,FUniversity, Dr Sweet said: "You've got
OL,9,Fall the countries in the tropics that
OL,10,Frely on healthy coral reefs for land
OL,11,Fprotection, they reduce the impacts of
OL,12,Fwaves, storms, hurricanes.
OL,14,F"If you lose those reefs, you're going
OL,15,Fto see significant amounts of
OL,16,Fflooding, of coastal erosion. You're
OL,17,Fgoing to get a huge displacement of
OL,18,Fpeople."
