OL,6,FHe continued: "What makes our work
OL,7,Fspecial (in our eyes) is our close
OL,8,Fcollaborations with other groups from
OL,9,Fcharities, trusts, universities and
OL,10,Feven the United Nations and other
OL,11,Fpolicy makers."
OL,13,FDr Till Rothig, who is a researcher
OL,14,Fadded: "This is exciting work on the
OL,15,Fforefront of international research.
OL,17,F"And maybe our work can help corals
OL,18,Fand their struggle with climate change
OL,19,Fat some stage ` but we really need to
OL,20,Fcut carbon emissions globally."
